ribute to their ability to generate B cell diversity and control infections. We found an expansion of genes associated with protection from various viruses in humans, differential expression of ERB isotypes across tissues, and two functional IgE genes.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Bartlett, Maggie L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Larson, Peter A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sanchez-Lockhart, Mariano", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Palacios, Gustavo", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/683855e89c03f9b9fda1b3778c18501a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/43e7bfc8cf93e522e9ff68ef38cafa03c156e4738dd01205c31b9d01c9c479bf", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/QUIWSQHL", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/QUIWSQHL", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/3ac0e445ca45198fa6d916df1046693a!/b322794-325357", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Conference paper", "type": "publication", "subtype": "conferencepaper"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/683855e89c03f9b9fda1b3778c18501a"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:QUIWSQHL"}, {"identifier": "10.3390/proceedings2020050142"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index"